Package: lay
Title: Yet Another Implementation of Rowwise Jobs
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Alexandre", "Courtiol", email = "alexandre.courtiol@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0637-2959")),
    person("Romain", "Francois", role = c("aut"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2444-4226"))
    )
Description: Create a vector by considering in turns each row of a data.frame or tibble as the vector input of some function(s).
    This makes the creation of new columns based on a rowwise operation both simple and efficient.
